      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers an affordable way into dependable transportation. It shows its age and is best suited for buyers who appreciate straightforward value, whether you need a practical commuter, a first car, or a project with potential. Priced to move and represented with honesty, it\u2019s a sensible opportunity for someone seeking maximum value at a low cost.",
