    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s best suited for someone looking for affordable wheels, a handy project, or a parts donor with potential. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it has a lot to offer the right buyer who doesn\u2019t mind giving it some TLC. If you\u2019re after a cheap way into ownership and appreciate a straightforward sale, this could be a great fit. Priced to reflect its condition and leave room for the next owner to make it their own.",
      "price": 6800.0,
