      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong project or budget daily candidate with solid bones and a drivetrain that still delivers dependable pull. Engine starts up, runs, and drives, with the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes this an appealing platform for someone handy with maintenance or looking for an affordable fixer-upper. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present, but the car offers honest utility, good parts value, and plenty of upside for the next owner. Priced to move for someone who wants inexpensive transportation or a worthwhile restoration base.",
